told her about Ben.

282
00:44:24,579 --> 00:44:25,999
Sonny, this is
no time for jokes.

283
00:44:26,205 --> 00:44:29,415
If you see any real rats,
tell your sister, all right?

284
00:44:30,459 --> 00:44:31,789
