377
00:53:08,560 --> 00:53:10,770
I told them
Henry fell in a rose bush.

378
00:53:12,564 --> 00:53:14,074
Probably wishes he did.

379
00:53:22,950 --> 00:53:24,370
I love you, Ben.

380
00:53:31,542 --> 00:53:33,212
Now, look, kirtland...

